import React, { Component } from 'react'

import {Card, Form, Button} from 'react-bootstrap';

export default class Exercise extends Component {

    render(){
        return(
            <Card className={"border border-dark bg-dark text-white"}>
                <Card.Header>
                    Add Exercise
                </Card.Header>
                <Card.Body>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group controlId="formExercise">
                        <Form.Label>Exercise Name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" className={"bg-dark text-white"} placeholder="Exercise Name" />
                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                        Enter the exercise name.
                        </Form.Text>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="formExercise">
                        <Form.Label>Exercise Duration</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" className={"bg-dark text-white"} placeholder="Exercise Duration" />
                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                        Enter the exercise duration.
                        </Form.Text>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="formExercise">
                        <Form.Label>Player Position</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" className={"bg-dark text-white"} placeholder="Player Position" />
                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                        Enter the player position for this exercise.
                        </Form.Text>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="formExercise">
                        <Form.Label>Coach Name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" className={"bg-dark text-white"} placeholder="Coach Name" />
                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                        Enter the name of the coach who will lead the exercise.
                        </Form.Text>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button size="lrg" variant="success" type="submit">
                        Submit
                    </Button>
                </Form>
                </Card.Body>
            </Card>
        );
    }
}
